<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>백엔드 개발자 포트폴리오</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@v2.16.0/devicon.min.css">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --black: #111;
      --gray-900: #1a1a1a;
      --gray-700: #444;
      --gray-500: #777;
      --gray-400: #999;
      --gray-300: #bbb;
      --gray-200: #ddd;
      --gray-100: #eee;
      --gray-50: #f5f5f5;
      --white: #fff;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--black);
      overflow: hidden;
      height: 100vh;
      width: 100vw;
    }

    /* ── SLIDE CONTAINER ── */
    .slides {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      overflow-y: auto;
      scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    .slides::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

    .slide {
      width: 100vw;
      min-height: 100vh;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 4rem 6rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }

    /* ── SLIDE INDICATOR ── */
    .indicator {
      position: fixed;
      top: 50%;
      right: 2rem;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--gray-200);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .dot.active {
      background: var(--black);
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* ── PAGE NUMBER ── */
    .page-num {
      position: fixed;
      top: 50%;
      right: 4rem;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      writing-mode: vertical-rl;
      text-orientation: mixed;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    /* ── TYPOGRAPHY ── */
    .mono {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    .label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════════
       SLIDE 1 — COVER
       ══════════════════════════════════════ */
    .cover {
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      padding-top: 2.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .cover-slogan {
      max-width: 680px;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .cover h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.5vw, 3.8rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .cover-keywords {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 1.15rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .cover-keywords span {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .cover-keywords span::before {
      content: '';
      display: inline-block;
      width: 4px;
      height: 4px;
      background: var(--gray-300);
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .cover-tech {
      width: min(900px, 100%);
      margin-top: 2.1rem;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .scroll-guide {
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: 2rem;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: inline-flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      animation: scroll-guide-float 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .scroll-guide::after {
      content: '';
      width: 1px;
      height: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gray-300), transparent);
    }

    .scroll-guide.hidden {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(10px);
    }

    @keyframes scroll-guide-float {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
      }
      35% {
        transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(14px);
      }
      70% {
        transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
      }
    }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════════
       SLIDE 2 — TECH STACK
       ══════════════════════════════════════ */
    .tech-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--gray-100);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .tech-cat {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .tech-cat-label {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .skill-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .skill-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 150px 62px minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 0.7rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .skill-name {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.45rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gray-700);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .skill-name i {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .skill-level {
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: 0.16rem;
      padding-top: 0.05rem;
    }

    .skill-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      background: var(--gray-200);
    }

    .skill-dot.filled {
      background: var(--black);
    }

    .skill-desc {
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--gray-500);
    }

    .pills {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.4rem;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.65rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--gray-700);
      background: var(--gray-50);
    }

    .pill i { font-size: 0.95rem; }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════════
       SLIDE 3, 4 — PROJECT DETAIL
       ══════════════════════════════════════ */
    .project-slide {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: start;
      padding-top: 3rem;
    }

    .project-left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .project-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .badge-award {
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      color: var(--gray-700);
    }

    .badge-role {
      background: var(--black);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .badge-context {
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      color: var(--gray-500);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .project-desc {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .role-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .role-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--gray-700);
    }

    .role-list li::before {
      content: '';
      width: 3px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--black);
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .project-right {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"],
    .slide[data-slide="4"] {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"] .project-slide,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .project-slide {
      align-items: stretch;
      gap: 1.75rem;
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"] .project-left,
    .slide[data-slide="2"] .project-right,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .project-left,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .project-right {
      gap: 0.85rem;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 10.5rem);
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"] .project-left .detail-panel,
    .slide[data-slide="2"] .project-right .detail-panel,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .project-left .detail-panel,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .project-right .detail-panel {
      padding: 1rem 1.15rem;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"] .gallery-shell,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .gallery-shell {
      flex: 1.05;
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"] .project-title,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .project-title {
      font-size: 1.85rem;
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"] .badge-context,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .badge-context {
      font-size: 0.64rem;
      padding: 0.28rem 0.55rem;
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"] .detail-panel-list,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .detail-panel-list {
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"] .detail-panel-list li,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .detail-panel-list li,
    .slide[data-slide="2"] .detail-panel-text,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .detail-panel-text {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      line-height: 1.48;
    }

    .slide[data-slide="2"] .gallery-card,
    .slide[data-slide="4"] .gallery-card {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 8.8;
    }

    .gallery-shell {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .gallery-viewport {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .gallery-track {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      overflow-x: auto;
      scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      scrollbar-width: none;
      padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
      touch-action: pan-x;
    }
    .gallery-track::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

    .gallery-shell.is-hinting .gallery-track {
      animation: gallery-peek 1.35s ease 0.35s 1;
    }

    .gallery-card {
      min-width: 100%;
      flex: 0 0 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gray-50), #fafafa);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
      padding: 1rem;
      color: var(--gray-300);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      scroll-snap-stop: always;
    }

    .gallery-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .gallery-btn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.08);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      color: var(--black);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1;
      cursor: pointer;
      z-index: 2;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.08);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }

    .gallery-btn:hover {
      background: var(--white);
      transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.04);
    }

    .gallery-btn:disabled {
      opacity: 0.4;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .gallery-btn.prev {
      left: 0.9rem;
    }

    .gallery-btn.next {
      right: 0.9rem;
    }

    .gallery-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .gallery-hint {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .gallery-count {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    @keyframes gallery-peek {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
      38%, 58% {
        transform: translateX(-40px);
      }
    }

    .detail-slide {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: start;
      padding-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    .detail-summary {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .detail-summary-kicker {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--gray-400);
    }

    .detail-summary-title {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.18;
    }

    .detail-summary-text {
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--gray-500);
    }

    .detail-summary-panel {
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--gray-50);
      padding: 1.25rem 1.35rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.95rem;
    }

    .summary-chip-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.45rem;
    }

    .summary-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.32rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gray-700);
    }

    .detail-summary-list {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .detail-panels {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .detail-panel {
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.35rem 1.5rem;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .detail-panel-label {
      font-size: 0.66rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .detail-panel-title {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    }

    .case-card-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
    }

    .case-step-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .case-step {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 3.4rem;
      padding: 0.26rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gray-600);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .detail-panel-text {
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--gray-500);
    }

    .detail-panel-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.45rem;
    }

    .detail-panel-list li {
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--gray-600, #666);
      padding-left: 0.9rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .detail-panel-list li::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0.65rem;
      left: 0;
      width: 4px;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--gray-300);
    }

    .img-placeholder {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16/10;
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border: 1px dashed var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--gray-300);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    /* arch flow */
    .arch-flow {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.3rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .arch-node {
      padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--gray-700);
    }

    .arch-arrow {
      color: var(--gray-300);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    /* metrics row */
    .metrics {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .metric {
      flex: 1;
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .metric .val {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .metric .key {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-top: 0.15rem;
    }

    .tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .tag {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: 3px;
      color: var(--gray-500);
    }

    /* challenge highlight */
    .challenge {
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--black);
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    }

    .challenge-label {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .challenge-text {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--gray-700);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════════
       SLIDE 5 — OTHER PROJECTS
       ══════════════════════════════════════ */
    .other-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1.25rem;
      max-width: 1000px;
    }

    .other-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .other-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--gray-300);
    }

    .other-card-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .other-card-name {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .other-card-role {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border-radius: 3px;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .other-card-desc {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .other-card .tags {
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════════
       SLIDE 6 — CREDENTIALS
       ══════════════════════════════════════ */
    .cred-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1.25rem;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .cred-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cred-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cred-name {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .cred-detail {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--gray-400);
    }

    .cred-year {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--gray-300);
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body { overflow: auto; }
      .slides {
        overflow-x: hidden;
        overflow-y: auto;
        scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
      }
      .slide {
        width: 100vw;
        padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
        scroll-snap-align: start;
      }
      .project-slide {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .detail-slide {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }
      .tech-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
      .skill-item {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 0.25rem;
      }
      .skill-level {
        padding-top: 0;
      }
      .gallery-card {
        min-width: 100%;
        flex-basis: 100%;
      }
      .gallery-btn {
        width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
      }
      .gallery-meta {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
      .other-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .cred-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .indicator,
      .page-num {
        display: none;
      }
      .scroll-guide {
        bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- INDICATOR -->
<div class="indicator" id="indicator"></div>

<!-- PAGE NUMBER -->
<div class="page-num" id="pageNum">1 / 9</div>

<!-- SLIDES -->
<div class="slides" id="slides">

  <!-- ═══ SLIDE 1: COVER ═══ -->
  <section class="slide cover" data-slide="1">
    <div class="cover-slogan">유지보수성과 정합성, 일관성을 바탕으로 금융 서비스를 구현합니다</div>
    <h1>Backend<br>Developer</h1>
    <div class="cover-keywords">
      <span>서버 설계</span>
      <span>인프라 구축</span>
      <span>금융 데이터</span>
      <span>실시간 시스템</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-tech">
      <div class="label">기술 스택</div>
      <div class="tech-grid">
        <div class="tech-cat">
          <div class="tech-cat-label">백엔드</div>
          <div class="skill-list">
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-name"><i class="devicon-spring-plain"></i>Spring Boot</div>
              <div class="skill-level"><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot"></span></div>
              <div class="skill-desc">REST API 설계, 도메인 분리, 배포 경험 중심으로 활용</div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-name">JPA</div>
              <div class="skill-level"><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot"></span></div>
              <div class="skill-desc">연관관계 매핑과 CRUD, 트랜잭션 중심 데이터 처리 경험</div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-name">Security</div>
              <div class="skill-level"><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot filled"></span><span class="skill-dot"></span><span class="skill-dot"></span></div>
              <div class="skill-desc">JWT 기반 인증·인가 구조를 구현하고 운영한 경험</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-cat">
          <div class="tech-cat-label">언어</div>
          <div class="skill-list">
            <div class="skill-item">
